data.description: Stunning, Immaculate, Open Floor plan!  4 Bedrooms and 3 Full Baths!  Potential in-law/teen suite upstairs.  1st floor owner's suite & 1st floor laundry.  First floor features a bonus/sun room with tons of window and light.  Neutral decor, move in condition!  Features include - Stainless appliances, gas stove, white cabinets, white 2 panel doors and trim, New lighting, luxury plank flooring, porcelain tile in baths, oversized kitchen island with peninsula/eating area in addition to a dining room.  Custom tile in owners suite, new shower door and shower faucet.  10 foot ceilings.  Shows like a model!
